Rajpal Singh had swallowed 140 coins, 150 nails and a handful of nuts and bolts over a three year period . 
  He also had swallowed screws, nails and magnets and complained of a stomach ache . 
  Doctors carried out an endoscopy to reveal hundreds of foreign objects in his stomach . 
  Mr Singh said he had swallowed the objects after falling into a depression . 
  He has had more than 240 procedures to remove the objects . 
  But he will still need another operation to remove all the metal . 
 